  <LinkList slot="sidebar" items={musicConcerts} orientation="vertical" />

  <p>
    I saw Sabrina Carpenter’s <em>Short n’ Sweet</em> tour at the Chase Center in November 2024. The show was split into three parts—“Short n’ Sweet,” “After Dark,” and “Don’t Touch That Dial”—and the production was huge: multi-level stage, big lighting cues, and slick transitions that made it feel like a musical in motion.
  </p>

